{"tid":759846,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞毒販懸賞54萬殺緝毒犬","createTime":"2018-07-29T04:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T08:20:02.000Z","uid":53379,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab0d045beae240fed4c51c14f1b44f895ab5b9e","tid":759846,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哥倫比亞毒販懸賞54萬殺緝毒犬 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞有毒販懸賞5.3萬英鎊（約54.6萬港元），殺死警方的一隻緝毒犬。該緝毒犬曾多次協助當地警方，於大西洋沿岸各大港口搗獲大量毒品，當中大部分為跨國犯罪集團計劃運至中南美洲的毒品，成為了一眾毒販的「眼中釘」。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞的緝毒犬Sombra（意指影子），為6歲的德國牧羊犬，多年來協助警方拘捕245名疑犯，其中一次在停車場搜出約4公噸將運離當地的毒品，亦曾經於圖爾博港口發現5.3公噸可卡因。自Sombra協助搗獲當地大型犯罪集Urabe&ntilde;os近10公噸可卡因後，他們懸賞5.3萬英鎊，指只要殺死Sombra，即可獲得賞金。<br />\n<br />\n由於毒販高價懸賞，Sombra現時暫退下前線，被安置於埃爾多拉多國際機場，當局亦安排人手保護她不受傷害。據報，6年前Urabe&ntilde;os曾懸賞美金500元（約3924港元）殺死一名警務人員，如今為了解決緝毒犬Sombra而大大增加了賞金，反映Sombra對其運作的影響之大。警方發言人形容，Sombra令跨國販毒集團「頭痛不已」。<br />\n<br />\n（每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180727/s00005/1532703158239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180727%2Fs00005%2F1532703158239&d=%2BE7Kq8wY7GpSYtDHNsGSHE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=46771adc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180727%2Fs00005%2F1532703158239&h=7a0ed6a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180727/s00005/1532703158239</a>"},{"pid":"c7cd0f66e4b493e46fad993482fde21fa3f3bd1f","tid":759846,"uid":172376,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"警察同警狗嘅分野"},{"pid":"caf54d0066923481c1dc86937be45aaf3b4450f3","tid":759846,"uid":40867,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T04:49:38.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞當地或考慮從香港引入專才"},{"pid":"dadbfa2c27392f168eed17c9fe848ebc947aa650","tid":759846,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d6bb5ff26bd46a94a3496e165b1cc4573594cd2","tid":759846,"uid":64308,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:02:20.000Z","msg":"佢都幾醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻狗退出前線<br />\n佢既目的已經達到咗<br />\n警察仲要保護隻狗<br />\n啲人殺唔到又唔洗比錢"},{"pid":"774fa48170a5871057bc867b54f4ad72e9f5edf2","tid":759846,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"Urabe&ntilde;os曾懸賞美金500元（約3924港元）殺死一名警務人員<br />\n大家唔好同我爭 今次我請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022b0dfb8395929ed88093ec45d2250e08bcbfab","tid":759846,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"幾公噸毒品 應該係緝毒犬都聞到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收埋一隻仲有下隻補上"},{"pid":"25ec7b2904876f18185d88b9f46d4804d54ed367","tid":759846,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"一隻狗仲有用過警察"},{"pid":"702dace21ffe6b53447e2975deaf896b990522a8","tid":759846,"uid":1181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"774fa48170a5871057bc867b54f4ad72e9f5edf2","tid":759846,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"Urabe&ntilde;os曾懸賞美金500元（約3924港元）殺死一名警務人員<br />\n大家唔好同我爭 今次我請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"即係平均3924港紙一條人命？嬲啊真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}